<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="pl6Aug1937"><font color="red">6 August 1937</font> <i>NLGC</i> (from G. Griffin to Paul L&eacute;on): I am very thankful for your letter and for the copy of transition (Winter number 26) &hellip; Just now I have also got a copy of my biography of D&apos;Annunzio which I shall return autographed as soon as I hear from you &hellip; I am writing to D&apos;Annunzio to request him to autograph Mr Joyce&apos;s copy of La Citt&agrave; Morta &hellip; I would like to see the proof sheets of the other copy of Transition which you mentioned, and shall take great care of it and return it promptly. </div>
